channel.title: How do i edit built in map objects?
channel.description: Ive looked in the client.java but there is only info about woodcutting but not location of already existing trees how do i remove them??? I am new to coding so thank you for your understanding :)

item.title: How do i edit built in map objects?
item.dc:creator: @alancarr123 alancarr123
item.description:
@alancarr123 wrote:

search in client.java for deletethatobject
type in the coords for the object, here this is how you would set it out.
deletethatobject(X, Y);
BTW its best if you use silab as you can see the coords.
